      "reason" : "REPEAT_HEAVY_DAY",
      "title" : "The day you brewed a triple-shot of bossa nova déjà vu",
      "description" : "Afternoon unfolded in a seamless loop: “Les eaux de mars,” “Café con Leche,” “Caminar bonito,” and Natalia Lafourcade’s boleros circled back again and again, stitched together by French jazz and bossa nova. Even as the hours blurred, the “cafecito” playlist kept the same gentle mood on repeat. 227 minutes, 67 tracks, 27 artists—your most repeat-heavy day of the year.",
