      "title" : "The day you built a time machine out of K-pop classics",
      "description" : "After a podcast break with Sydnee Washington, you dove headlong into a marathon of iconic old K-pop—Girls' Generation, SHINee, BIGBANG, and more, looping through 71 tracks by 37 artists. 257 minutes, 1 podcast, 1 episode—your most K-pop-packed day of the year, outpacing even your annual top genre stats.",
